>6 (2x-1)+ 3(3x+4) = 2 (1-4x)
>12x - 6 + 9x + 12 = 2 - 8x
>21x + 5 =  - 6x   <-- THIS IS THE FIRST WRONG EQUATION
>+6x        + 6x
>27x + 5 =  0
